<view class="page">
  <view class="header-section">
    <view class="header-icon-wrap">
      <text class="header-icon-text">🔔</text>
    </view>
    <text class="header-title">消息推送订阅设置</text>
    <text class="header-desc">开启您需要的消息通知，及时掌握课程动态</text>
  </view>

  <view class="subscribe-all-card" bindtap="onSubscribeAll">
    <text class="sa-text">一键订阅全部通知</text>
    <text class="sa-sub" wx:if="{{unsubscribedCount > 0}}">还有 {{unsubscribedCount}} 个未授权，点击开始授权（每次最多3个）</text>
    <text class="sa-sub" wx:else>全部已授权 ✓</text>
  </view>

  <view class="settings-section">
    <view class="section-label">通知类型</view>
    <view class="settings-card">
      <block wx:for="{{templatesWithStatus}}" wx:key="key">
        <view class="setting-item">
          <view class="setting-info">
            <text class="setting-name">{{item.name}}</text>
            <text class="setting-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="setting-action">
            <text class="setting-status subscribed" wx:if="{{item.subscribed}}">✓ 已订阅</text>
            <text class="setting-status once" wx:elif="{{item.onceAccepted}}">已授权(一次性)</text>
            <text class="setting-status rejected" wx:elif="{{item.rejected}}">已拒绝</text>
            <view class="setting-status-btn" wx:else catchtap="onSubscribeSingle" data-id="{{item.id}}" data-index="{{index}}">
              <text>待授权</text>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class="setting-divider" wx:if="{{index < templatesWithStatus.length - 1}}"></view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="tips-section">
    <text class="tips-text">💡 微信订阅消息为一次性消费授权，每授权一次仅能接收一条通知。"已授权(一次性)"表示配额可能已消耗，如需长期接收请勾选「总是保持以上选择」。每次点击最多授权3个，如有剩余请再次点击「一键订阅」。</text>
  </view>
</view>
